{'category': 'News', 'content': '<h1>关于申报2016年度“四川大学O2Micro奖助学金”的通知 <span>发布时间：2016-10-31 13:32:59, 已阅读：1157次</span></h1> \n<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">全院全日制研究生、本科生：<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">四川大学<span lang="EN-US">O2Micro</span>奖助学金系凹凸电子（成都）有限公司为支持教育事业的发展，鼓励学生潜心向学、帮助学习努力但家庭贫困的学生顺利完成学业，在我校、针对我院研究生、本科生设立的专项奖助学金。<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">现根据奖助学金的设立协议以及学院学生工作组讨论，现通知申报<span lang="EN-US">2016</span>年度该专项奖助学金事宜如下：<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">一．奖助学金评选对象<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、我院注册在校的全日制研究生、本科生。不包括政法干警法律硕士、政法干警二学位班本科生和在职法律硕士研究生。<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、非<span lang="EN-US">2013</span>级本科生和<span lang="EN-US">2014</span>级硕士研究生<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">3</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、具体对象范围：<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">A</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">．家庭经济困难但努力学习的学生<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">B</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">．品学兼优，成绩突出的学生<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">二．评选期间：<span lang="EN-US">2015</span>年<span lang="EN-US">9</span>月<span lang="EN-US">1</span>日至<span lang="EN-US">2016</span>年<span lang="EN-US">8</span>月<span lang="EN-US">31</span>日<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">三．拟评奖助学金的名额、额度及相关条件<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">（一）奖学金<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、<span lang="EN-US">10</span>名，每人<span lang="EN-US">RMB1500.00</span>元。<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、申请奖学金的同学，应依凹凸电子（成都）有限公司的要求，为其做指定的专项书面报告，并经甲方确认。具体要求附后。<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">书面报告方向：外籍员工劳动纠纷法律解决途径研究<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">（二）助学金<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">1</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、<span lang="EN-US">15</span>名，每人<span lang="EN-US">RMB1000.00</span>元。<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">2</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">、获助同学，依凹凸电子（成都）有限公司的要求，可自愿撰写指定专项书面报告，并经甲方确认。具体要求附后。<a name="_GoBack"></a><span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">书面报告方向：外籍员工劳动纠纷法律解决途径研究<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">四．申报时间<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">符合条件且有意申报者，当于<span lang="EN-US">2016</span>年<span lang="EN-US">11</span>月<span lang="EN-US">4</span>日<span lang="EN-US">17</span>：<span lang="EN-US">00</span>前递交纸质申请材料至各年级、专业辅导员处。学院汇总后将及时评审，并报凹凸公司确认。<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">特此通知！<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-indent: 28pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体" lang="EN-US">\n  <o:p>\n   &nbsp;\n  </o:p></span></p> \n<p style="text-align: right; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class="MsoNormal" align="right"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">中共四川大学法学院党委学生工作组<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<p style="text-align: right; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt" class="MsoNormal" align="right"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体">二零一六年十月三十一日<span lang="EN-US">\n   <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> \n<div> \n <br> \n <table style="margin-left: 50px;" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" class="file"> \n  <tbody>\n   <tr> \n    <td colspan="2" class="header">相关附件</td> \n   </tr> \n   <tr> \n    <td width="75%">文件名称: <font style="font-size:14px;">四川大学O2Micro奖助学金评申请表.pdf</font> </td> \n    <td width="25%"> <a target="_blank" class="download" href="http://law.scu.edu.cn/download?portalId=725&amp;aid=74852&amp;filename=2016103113345896629.pdf"> <font face="Wingdings" size="3">&lt;</font>下载 </a> </td> \n   </tr> \n  </tbody>\n </table> \n</div>', 'time': '2016-10-31T05:32:59Z', 'title': '关于申报2016年度“四川大学O2Micro奖助学金”的通知', 'academy': '法学院', 'originURL': 'http://law.scu.edu.cn/detail.jsp?portalId=725&cid=8385&nextcid=8572&aid=74852'}